{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5744958e5f","title":"“党委违反中央政策”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"eab692e573","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"5744958e5f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0aeba49c5c","name":"龙国坤"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"9b3fd4c2d0","name":"李康年"},{"id":"b00ac235f2","name":"付锟"},{"id":"cd6d1d2c70","name":"李燕吉"},{"id":"ef186de7f6","name":"伍奂中"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"411615c9bb","type":"title","text":"“党委违反中央政策”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"915cc6b88d","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院李维干李燕吉伍奂中龙国坤付锟","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"48b98397b0","type":"paragraph","text":"李维干说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"cc5c1ee2fc","type":"paragraph","text":"“党委违反中央政策把关于知识分子的团结教育，改造政策变成打击，排挤，赶走的政策。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"2ebefadc38","type":"paragraph","text":"李燕吉说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"cb935f36b0","type":"paragraph","text":"“党用人不重才干。高级知识分子今后会减少了，也伤了父母的心，不希望孩子深造了。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"553a6c677b","type":"paragraph","text":"伍奂中说：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"7bb50f9c1e","type":"paragraph","text":"“不管其人如何，达到教授水平就应给教授称号，教授是学衔，美国教授还是教授。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"a275fb2a18","type":"paragraph","text":"龙国坤说：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"01acd5a6a3","type":"paragraph","text":"“钱伟长是学术上骗子，为什么应得奖金？一下子棒一气，一下子垮下来，斯大林也是这样，什么事总是这样。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"3bf5420ce9","type":"paragraph","text":"“老干部和知识分子之间的矛盾，只有在党的干部提高科学文化水平成为内行的时候才能解决。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"178051b144","type":"paragraph","text":"付锟说：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"},{"id":"d50719ccd1","type":"paragraph","text":"“思想改造是不必要的，伤害了知识分子的自尊心。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f"}],"page":{"id":"7163174348","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5744958e5f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}